
# type(scope): short description
# types:
# feat     - new feature                                         - feat: add user login endpoint
# fix      - bug fix                                             - fix: prevent memory leak on image upload
# docs     - documentation changes                               - docs: update API rate limit information
# style    - code style changes (formatting, etc.)               - style: format code with Black linter
# refactor - code change without fixing bugs or adding features  - refactor: extract database logic to a repository
# perf     - performance improvement                             - perf: optimize user query for faster load times
# test     - adding or updating tests                            - test: add unit tests for new payment service
# chore    - maintenance tasks                                   - chore: update dependencies in requirements.txt
# build    - changes to build tools or dependencies              - build: update Dockerfile for production environment
# ci       - continuous integration setup                        - ci: add new deployment step to GitHub Actions
# example:
# feat(auth): add login endpoint
